@model AdminPasswordChangedMailTemplate
@inject ICofoundryMailTemplateHelper Cofoundry

@{
    Layout = AdminMailTemplatePath.LayoutPath_Text;
    var applicationName = Cofoundry.Sanitizer.Sanitize(Model.ApplicationName);
}

Hello,

Your password for the @applicationName content
management system been changed. If this was not you, please contact the
site administrator.

The username registered for this account is @Cofoundry.Sanitizer.Sanitize(Model.Username)

Login here: @Html.Raw(Cofoundry.Routing.ToAbsolute(Model.LoginPath))

This message was automatically generated by the @applicationName site.
